Package net.sf.mmm.client.ui.impl.gwt.widget.window Description

Contains the implementation for window widgets using GWT.

Client UI Impl GWT Widget Window

This package contains the implementation of net.sf.mmm.client.ui.api.widget.window using GWT (Google Web Toolkit).
